videos.headline: Joe Burrow's NFL draft profile
videos.description: Take a look at highlights from Joe Burrow's senior season at LSU, during which he won the Heisman Trophy and led the Tigers to a No. 1 ranking.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NFL Draft Highlight (The best of Joe Burrow's Heisman season) 2019/12/11 ESHEET ENHL

videos.headline: Jefferson dives for first LSU score
videos.description: LSU drives right down the field on Oklahoma as Justin Jefferson dives for the end zone on a 19-yard touchdown to open the scoring.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jefferson dives for first LSU score) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Lamb's circus catch sets up OU TD
videos.description: Oklahoma's CeeDee Lamb hauls in an unreal one-handed catch to set up a 3-yard Kennedy Brooks touchdown late in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lamb's circus catch sets up OU TD) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Burrow scrambles, finds Marshall in end zone
videos.description: Joe Burrow scrambles to avoid a defender, then threads the needle to Terrace Marshall Jr. in the end zone for the LSU touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow scrambles, finds Marshall in end zone) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Riley fired up after no-call on potential pass interference
videos.description: Jadon Haselwood attempts to catch Jalen Hurts' pass, but is hindered by a LSU defender with no penalty called by the referees.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Riley fired up after no-call on potential pass interference) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow somehow finds Marshall for the catch
videos.description: Joe Burrow scrambles all the way to the sideline and somehow completes the pass to Terrace Marshall Jr. for the 24-yard gain.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow somehow finds Marshall for the catch) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Burrow, Jefferson connect for 2nd TD of day
videos.description: Joe Burrow throws a dime to Justin Jefferson as LSU scores their third touchdown of the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow, Jefferson connect for 2nd TD of day) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Radley-Hiles ejected for targeting on cheap shot
videos.description: Brendan Radley-Hiles is ejected for targeting after taking a shot to a defenseless Clyde Edwards-Helaire in the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Radley-Hiles ejected for targeting on cheap shot) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow and Jefferson connect for a third TD
videos.description: Joe Burrow scrambles and goes deep to Justin Jefferson for the 42-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow and Jefferson connect for a third TD) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Vincent rises for the incredible INT for LSU
videos.description: Jalen Hurts attempts the trick-play pass, but leaves the ball in the air too long and is picked off by LSU defender Kary Vincent Jr.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Vincent rises for the incredible INT for LSU) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Jefferson hauls in record 4th TD of first half
videos.description: Justin Jefferson ties the FBS bowl record with four receiving touchdowns in a half as No. 1 LSU takes it to No. 4 Oklahoma.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jefferson hauls in record 4th TD of first half) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Hurts calls his own number for TD
videos.description: Jalen Hurts keeps the ball himself and rushes into the end zone for an Oklahoma touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurts calls his own number for TD) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Moss catches Burrow's 6th TD of first half
videos.description: Thaddeus Moss, son of NFL Hall of Famer Randy Moss, is the recipient of Joe Burrow's sixth touchdown of the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Moss catches Burrow's 6th TD of first half) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Burrow throws CFP-record 7th TD in first half
videos.description: Joe Burrow sets a College Football Playoff record, throwing his seventh touchdown of the game, all in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow throws CFP-record 7th TD in first half) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Burrow slings 7 TDs in the first half vs. Oklahoma
videos.description: Joe Burrow comes out firing, throwing seven touchdowns -- including four to Justin Jefferson -- in a dominant first-half performance.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Burrow slings 7 TDs in the first half vs. Oklahoma) 2019/12/28 SOTFULL

videos.headline: Burrow runs in for TD
videos.description: Joe Burrow goes away from throwing touchdowns and instead runs in for one to start the second half for LSU.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow runs in for TD) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Hurts flies for TD
videos.description: On fourth down, Jalen Hurts flies just past the pylon to grab the third touchdown for the Sooners.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurts flies for TD) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Hurts jogs off the field for final time
videos.description: Jalen Hurts jogs off the field, finishing his college career.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurts jogs off the field for final time) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Orgeron: Ensminger is getting the game ball
videos.description: LSU head coach Ed Orgeron says the game ball will go to offensive coordinator Steve Ensminger, who lost his daughter-in-law earlier on Saturday.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCFInterview (Orgeron: Ensminger is getting the game ball) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Burrow: This was expected from us
videos.description: Joe Burrow explains that it's going to be a lot of fun playing in New Orleans for the CFP National Championship.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF interview (Burrow: This was expected from us) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow's dominant 8-TD game sends LSU to title game
videos.description: Joe Burrow throws for seven touchdowns and runs for one, leading LSU to a dominant win over Oklahoma 63-28.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Burrow’s dominant 8-TD game sends LSU to title game) 2019/12/28 SOTFULL

videos.headline: Hurts: Loss to LSU is not a good feeling
videos.description: Jalen Hurts says he failed to fulfill his promise to Lincoln Riley that he would win Oklahoma a national championship.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser (Hurts: Loss to LSU is not a good feeling) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Burrow: 8-TD performance wasn't my sharpest game
videos.description: Joe Burrow reflects on his historic eight-touchdown performance against Oklahoma in the Chick-Fil-A Peach Bowl, admitting he's still seeking the "perfect" game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Burrow: 8-TD performance wasn't my sharpest game) 2019/12/28 ESHEET SVP

videos.headline: Burrow has legendary performance in Peach Bowl win
videos.description: Joe Burrow puts on a clinic in LSU's Peach Bowl win vs. Oklahoma, tossing a College Football Playoff-record seven touchdowns and adding a rushing score.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Burrow has legendary performance in Peach Bowl win) 2019/12/28 ESHEET
